snippet: With two unheralded players already victorious in the Champions Tour’s majors, some pros are wondering who will be next when the United States Senior Open begins Thursday.
abstract: Some pros are wondering who will be next golfer to breakthrough when the United States Senior Open begins, after two unheralded players have won in the Champions Tour’s majors; to some observers, the lackluster record of many distinguished pros on the senior circuit defies explanation.
lead_paragraph: With two unheralded players already victorious in the Champions Tour’s majors, some pros are wondering who will be next when the United States Senior Open begins Thursday.
